{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Raise the legal age to buy and consume alcohol to 25",
        "additional_details": "As someone who knows the risks of alcohol and its impact on people, I think urgent action should be taken. With exam season in full swing, young people who hit the bottle if they fail their exams could be risking their own health for a substance with an unpleasant taste.",
        "background": "Raising the drinking age to 25 could help protect young adults\u2019 developing brains, reduce alcohol-related accidents, and ease pressure on the NHS. Studies have found later drinking onset decreases addiction risk and improves public health, making this policy a smart, preventative measure.",
